q0.question: How did Tien lose his parents?
q0.recall: Tien lost his parents in a massacre where he became the sole survivor.
q0.vectordb: Tien lost his parents in a massacre orchestrated by Lord Rajasena. He was the only survivor and managed to escape with deep vengeance in his heart.
